{"snp5.13:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.13 ","snp5.13:0.2":"Bhadravudhamanavapuccha ","snp5.13:1.1":"“Okanjaham tanhacchidam anejam, ","snp5.13:1.2":"(iccayasma bhadravudho) ","snp5.13:1.3":"Nandinjaham oghatinnam vimuttam; ","snp5.13:1.4":"Kappanjaham abhiyace sumedham, ","snp5.13:1.5":"Sutvana nagassa apanamissanti ito. ","snp5.13:2.1":"Nanajana janapadehi sangata, ","snp5.13:2.2":"Tava vira vakyam abhikankhamana; ","snp5.13:2.3":"Tesam tuvam sadhu viyakarohi, ","snp5.13:2.4":"Tatha hi te vidito esa dhammo”. ","snp5.13:3.1":"“Adanatanham vinayetha sabbam, ","snp5.13:3.2":"(bhadravudhati bhagava ","snp5.13:3.3":"Uddham adho tiriyancapi majjhe; ","snp5.13:3.4":"Yam yanhi lokasmimupadiyanti, ","snp5.13:3.5":"Teneva maro anveti jantum. ","snp5.13:4.1":"Tasma pajanam na upadiyetha, ","snp5.13:4.2":"Bhikkhu sato kincanam sabbaloke; ","snp5.13:4.3":"Adanasatte iti pekkhamano, ","snp5.13:4.4":"Pajam imam maccudheyye visattan”ti. ","snp5.13:4.5":"Bhadravudhamanavapuccha dvadasama. "}